Package: metawoRld
Title: A Framework for Managing Data in Living Systematic Reviews
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Anders Hagen", "Jarmund", , "anders.h.jarmund@ntnu.no", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3923-1637"))
Description: Provides a structured environment for creating, validating, and managing data for living systematic reviews. It facilitates reproducible data storage using YAML and CSV formats, and supports the generation of project websites to display review progress and findings. It is designed to integrate with the DataFindR package for AI-assisted data extraction from scientific literature.
